  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A more grown-up Match 3 Game with thought provoking silent story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use fire, water, air, rock, lightning magic and sword to defeat enemies and to protect innocent. <br>Overcome obstacles like stones, sand, ice, roots, snakes, worms, swamp, blood and wildfire. Open chests, collect coins, buy boosters and bombs. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unveil a dramatic story by going through 106 interesting levels, each with unique adventure and background.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautifully animated gems, powerful boosters and bombs.<br>Dramatic soundtrack! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A single player game.<br>Pay once and play, no hidden payments, no microtransactions.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A more grown-up Match 3 Game with thought provoking silent story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use fire, water, air, rock, lightning magic and sword to defeat enemies and to protect innocent. <br>Overcome obstacles like stones, sand, ice, roots, snakes, worms, swamp, blood and wildfire. Open chests, collect coins, buy boosters and bombs. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unveil a dramatic story by going through 106 interesting levels, each with unique adventure and background.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautifully animated gems, powerful boosters and bombs.<br>Dramatic soundtrack! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A single player game.<br>Pay once and play, no hidden payments, no microtransactions.</p>",
